### 1. 核心路由规则

本仓库（项目）不适用单一的免费开源许可证。仓库内资产已按「双资产分层许可隔离架构」进行法理切分，任何主体复制、修改、分发或开展商用运营，必须严格依照资产类别匹配对应的许可证。

### 1. Core Routing Rules

This repository DOES NOT apply a single unified free open-source license. Assets within this repository have been legally segmented under a "Dual-Asset Tiered Licensing Isolation Architecture". Any party copying, modifying, distributing, or conducting commercial operations shall strictly comply with the specific license matched to each asset category.

