**【计算机源代码类资产】**

单独适用根目录下的 `LICENSE-APACHE` 文件（即 Apache License 2.0）。其复制、修改、分发本身仅受该开源许可约束，完整许可文本详见根目录 `LICENSE-APACHE` 文件。

**[Computer Source Code Assets]**

Governed exclusively by the `LICENSE-APACHE` file (Apache License 2.0) in the root directory. The act of copying, modifying, and distributing the code itself is subject solely to said permissive license. The full license text is available in the `LICENSE-APACHE` file in the root directory.

